Package: SimiCviz
Type: Package
Title: Visualization Tools for Gene Regulatory Network Analysis
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Irene","Marin-Goni",
    role = c( "aut","cre"),
    email = "imarin.4@alumni.unav.es", 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5060-0712")))
Description: 
    Visualization and export utilities for SimiC and SimiCPipeline outputs.
    The package focuses on importing SimiC-style results (e.g., weights, AUC
    metrics) from pickle/CSV files, processing and generating publication-ready
    plots (networks, heatmaps, distributions) and tables saved into a reproducible, 
    ordered directory hierarchy.
